high_descs: Walk straight, then right to face the black desk at the other side of the room.
Pick up the remote in the middle.
Turn around then walk to the left to face the other side of the ottoman.
Place the remote on the ottoman.
Turn to the right and go straight to face the black desk.
Pick up the remote to the left.
Turn around then walk to the left to face the other side of the ottoman.
Place the remote on the ottoman.
anns.task_desc: Place both remotes from the black table on the black ottoman.

high_descs: Walk to the ottoman then turn right and walk to the small table with three remotes on it that's in front of you to your left.
Pick up the remote that's near the front edge of the small table.
Turn around and walk to the ottoman then step left and take a step forward then turn right to face the ottoman.
Put the remote horizontally near the bottom right corner of the face of the ottoman.
Go back to where you got the first remote.
Pick up the remote that's in front of you.
Go back to where you put the first remote.
Put the remote to the left of the first one with about half a remote's length between them,.
anns.task_desc: Put two remotes on the ottoman.

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk forward and face the black table to the left.
Pick up the closest remote on the table.
Turn around and walk forward to face the left side of the table in front of the chair.
Place the remote on the corner of the black table in front of the chair.
Turn to the right and walk forward and face the black table to the left.
Pick up the remote on the left side of the black table.
Turn around and walk forward to face the left side of the table in front of the chair.
Place the remote to the left of the other remote.
anns.task_desc: To move two remotes, one at a time from a black side table to the table in front of the chair.
